{"tid":1676357,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"LIHKG Misic Awards 2019 連登音樂排行榜頒獎典禮(主post)","createTime":"2019-10-26T11:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T08:30:08.000Z","uid":125502,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"991734de26b5f46760ce5af7816d731c5ce9a0b0","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">LIHKG Music Awards 2019 連登音樂排行榜頒獎典禮</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MfPqAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MfPqAa.jpg&h=773b4cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有鑑於連登與香港樂壇及本地歌手的活動愈趨頻繁，加上最近連登討論區在社會的，曝光率亦十分高所以為了能夠表揚 本地樂壇出色的貢獻，決定舉辦一個屬於連登一人一票的音樂頒獎典禮，音樂頒獎典禮又全年登會員一同參與一人一票選出自己喜愛的~<br />\n<br />\n提名期：即日起至11月10日<br />\n首輪投票日期：11月11日至11月30日(並且即時於31日凌晨點算結果)<br />\n&middot;<br />\n#連登 #音樂 #廣東歌 #連登音樂台 #連登音樂排行榜頒獎典禮2019<br />\n&middot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【連登十大最愛金曲獎】</strong></span><br />\n歡迎到指定post寫上歌名及歌手以便提名<br />\n任何人士提名選出候選名單，最高票數的20名就會進入第二輪投票，選出頭十名作為十強，當中包括第一名第二名及第三名的金銀銅獎。<br />\n<br />\n提名方式在該post下方留言歌名及歌手(需使用繁體中文，如果歌名為英文則不在此限)如果有重複提名，則計算第一個提名之「正負皮」分數， 分數將會計算「正皮」減去「負皮」後的淨值。<br />\n<br />\n二十強以同樣方式運作，直至選出十大名單<br />\n由於數目量大，因此候選名單片段只會節錄部分歌曲，排名不分先後:-) 。<br />\n觀看候選名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/odVK6lKNwmI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FodVK6lKNwmI&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=64f832dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/odVK6lKNwmI</a><br />\n&middot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【最佳music video獎項】</strong></span><br />\n在指定的post內貼上youtube music video link作為提名，及後根據同樣計算「正負皮淨值」後選出金、銀、銅獎，所有music video以 youtube上顯示的上傳日期為標準，全部要於2019年內才算有效。<br />\n&middot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【最佳現場演繹大獎】</strong></span><br />\n選出2019年其中一個你最喜愛的現場演繹，包括售票的音樂會或演唱會，大小型也可，不限於紅館，<br />\n而任何於2019年舉行之音樂會或演唱會，只需其中任何至少一場在2019年內舉行就符合資格，因此跨年演唱會亦可計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n片段提及候選名單排名不分先後<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kVLMytyCBLg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkVLMytyCBLg&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=063f1aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kVLMytyCBLg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【連登最愛專輯大獎】</strong></span><br />\n在指定的post內投票選出本年度專輯大獎得主，包括實體專輯的大碟、EP、LP 以及數位專輯， 提名片段只顯示截至截稿前2019年所有已推出的實體專輯。<br />\n&middot;<br />\n連登最愛專輯大獎候選名單包括：<br />\n仲間 周國賢<br />\nCurations Robynn and Kendy<br />\n浮世繪 李倖倪<br />\n黃妍說 黃妍<br />\nIn His Name 衛蘭<br />\n我們都是這樣長大的 鄭秀文<br />\n(排名不分先後)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ovH8y7jpimA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FovH8y7jpimA&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=d3ede72e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ovH8y7jpimA</a><br />\n&middot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【連登討論區最愛男歌手、女歌手獎】</strong></span><br />\n在分別兩個指定的post內提名，並且即時透過計算「正負皮淨值」選出金銀銅獎，提名需要是繁體中文全名或英文全名才有效，部份音樂人可能只有英文藝名，因此英文名亦可接受。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【連登討論區最愛組合樂隊大獎】</strong></span><br />\n不論是否獨立音樂人，在指定的post內以與男女歌手同樣方式提名，並且即時透過計算「正負皮淨值」選出一個獎項。<br />\n&middot;<br />\n稍後已經可以在獨立post提名歌曲獎(20強)及男、女、組合歌手(最後五強)<br />\n請各位踴躍參與~"},{"pid":"24e6a92a225bee4d15cfe39b5575893d5f3e70ec","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登十大最愛金曲獎歡迎排名</strong></span><br />\n▲前往娛樂台▲<br />\n然後喺留言度放低一首今年推出嘅廣東歌<br />\n提名期至11月15日，之後就會計算「正皮減負皮淨值」<br />\n▲▲▲<br />\nLIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登十大最愛金曲奬提名post)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676389</a>"},{"pid":"b7dc6d58cf0a64bd8aab44feafe45857a1964808","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登討論區最愛男歌手五強提名開始<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n請前往娛樂台▲<br />\n提名後，如果有重複只會計算第一個留言正負皮淨值，正負皮淨值即是正皮減負皮的數值，多謝各位踴躍參與！<br />\n▲▲▲<br />\nLIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登討論區最愛男歌手五強提名post)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676439</a>"},{"pid":"7cff91929fc2bb4aabccf625621e1c67c1d4fcf4","tid":1676357,"uid":55800,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"g持<br />\n但點解專輯嗰度得咁少<br />\n安仔 per se 雷同二友 鄧小巧 陳蕾 serrini 盧凱彤 Nowhere Boys Dear Jane 黃淑蔓 仲有好多單位今年都有出碟喎<br />\n其他獎入圍準則都可以再清楚啲，例如男女組合獎係咪2019年要有出歌先有資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b4c3d3bcb85dce5c09c3ad3f1876e70a27975f","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cff91929fc2bb4aabccf625621e1c67c1d4fcf4","tid":1676357,"uid":55800,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"g持<br />\n但點解專輯嗰度得咁少<br />\n安仔 per se 雷同二友 鄧小巧 陳蕾 serrini 盧凱彤 Nowhere Boys Dear Jane 黃淑蔓 仲有好多單位今年都有出碟喎<br />\n其他獎入圍準則都可以再清楚啲，例如男女組合獎係咪2019年要有出歌先有資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"要有出歌先有資格呀<br />\n同埋大家提名嗰陣就可以寫自己鍾意嘅專輯<br />\n因為我啲片同埋我啲字可能有遺漏，只要check過係今年出嘅碟大家就可以寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a288708afd5bb741b50dc408febfd257b74262","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登討論區最愛女歌手五強提名開始<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n請前往娛樂台▲<br />\n提名後，如果有重複只會計算第一個留言正負皮淨值，正負皮淨值即是正皮減負皮的數值，多謝各位踴躍參與！<br />\n▲▲▲<br />\nLIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登討論區最愛女歌手五強提名post)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676622</a>"},{"pid":"c69a893ae62079783043843578e2837169f1fefb","tid":1676357,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9c5Um.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9c5Um.gif&h=4ad4d108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9563456046a8d3d26fae54c22b3051f761d6918","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"11月10號截止現有提名<br />\n於公佈結果後，11月15日展開五強投票"},{"pid":"5dc879da247b36957ed9dbb9ae8f2859ccade763","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登討論區最愛男歌手</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五強結果</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyKCfXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyKCfXU.jpg&h=4a45996e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男歌手五強片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UiUBl4L4hug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUiUBl4L4hug&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=9877eb6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UiUBl4L4hug</a><br />\n<br />\n五強男女歌手投票於15號開始，於男女歌手獨立投票post，尋找所屬歌手歌名留言，並按下正皮，最終會計算「正負皮淨值」分數，並選出金銀銅獎"},{"pid":"3242272f9a9e4683394d5ac3af5f94791c133210","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登討論區最愛女歌手</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五強結果</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVfmHEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVfmHEg.jpg&h=5d1fa29b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女歌手五強片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xYafWKMmTPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxYafWKMmTPY&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=b16e1ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xYafWKMmTPY</a><br />\n<br />\n五強男女歌手投票於15號開始，於男女歌手獨立投票post，尋找所屬歌手歌名留言，並按下正皮，最終會計算「正負皮淨值」分數，並選出金銀銅獎"},{"pid":"336cd02e8aa3b0a33684337347345456d438a6af","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:00:15.000Z","msg":"女歌手五強片段已經更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j7S8Lp4575k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj7S8Lp4575k&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=7ff43d2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j7S8Lp4575k</a>"},{"pid":"cf80cb3e7012e1637b7fb2ec945ce6f4c5a6dd35","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登十大最愛金曲獎</strong><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">二十強</span></strong>結果公佈</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FRMWSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FRMWSa.png&h=5f5766d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3351e9352299704a84999a03192636171e67e2e","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T06:51:59.000Z","msg":"較早前因為區選同埋其他更重要嘅活動所以暫時擱置，而家又因為有其他更新嘅歌曲推出，所以建議重新再提名投票【連登十大最愛金曲獎】<br />\n有冇人有異議？"},{"pid":"c35b8926267152dae6dcc55f25519175d4f335d6","tid":1676357,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d33dfb1528a282c6f4595da7609a55c408967689","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c35b8926267152dae6dcc55f25519175d4f335d6","tid":1676357,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"今晚，十強金曲重新提名<br />\n另外【現場演繹】【最佳專輯】以及【最愛組合】亦會在今晚開post投票"},{"pid":"02aea81faf73d3fc852e21dfcb0b5c89e7c22835","tid":1676357,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>【連登討論區最愛組合樂隊大獎】</strong><br />\n 直接投票，根據「正負皮淨值」選出最高分數<br />\n<strong>【連登十大最愛金曲】</strong>及<strong>【連登最佳music video獎】</strong><br />\n選出入圍20強，然後再選出十大<br />\n<strong>【連登最佳現場演繹獎】</strong><br />\n直接投票，根據「正負皮淨值」選出最高分數"},{"pid":"a81875c62757a7bc2f9117b168b76bab719a3209","tid":1676357,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"無紫荊狂想曲， 無阿李既天真<br />\n到底點題名？"}]}